Class LogParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.demo.LogParser

  • public class LogParser
extends java.lang.Object
    Parser Class, used to hold the Log string and split it, to generate the list of LogEntry, which are also stored in the class.
    The LogEntry are created using LogEntryFactory
